<% content_for :title, "세무상식 - 일잘러 필수 상식" %>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes slideInLeft {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }
  @keyframes bounceIn {
    0% { transform: scale(0.3); opacity: 0; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
    70% { transform: scale(0.9); }
    100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
  }
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% { background-position: -200% 0; }
    100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
  }
  @keyframes floatEmoji {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-4px) rotate(-3deg); }
    75% { transform: translateY(2px) rotate(3deg); }
  }

  .tax-page { min-height:100vh; background:#f5f5f5; padding-bottom:100px; }
  
  .tax-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b 0%, #312e81 40%, #4f46e5 100%);
    padding: 28px 20px 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tax-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -40px;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .tax-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px; left: 20px;
    width: 100px; height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  }

  .tax-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin: 0 16px 16px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-left: 4px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  .tax-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .tax-card:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

  .tax-card-icon {
    font-size: 40px;
    display: inline-block;
    animation: floatEmoji 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .tax-card-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    margin-right: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .tax-card-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .tax-card-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-left: 36px;
  }

  .tax-item {
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }
  .tax-item:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
  }

  .tax-badge-ok {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #dcfce7;
    color: #166534;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tax-badge-no {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #fef2f2;
    color: #991b1b;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tax-badge-warn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #fef3c7;
    color: #92400e;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .tax-highlight-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
    border: 1.5px solid #93c5fd;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .tax-danger-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
    border: 1.5px solid #fca5a5;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .tax-tip-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
    border: 1.5px solid #86efac;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .tax-bottom-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
    margin: 0 16px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>

<div class="tax-page">

  <!-- 헤더 -->
  <div class="tax-hero">
    <div style="position:relative; z-index:2;">
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:16px;">
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" style="color:white; text-decoration:none;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <div style="font-size:18px; font-weight:900; color:white;">세무상식</div>
      </div>

      <div style="animation: bounceIn 0.8s ease;">
        <div style="font-size:42px; margin-bottom:8px;">💡</div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:22px; font-weight:900; color:white; line-height:1.4; margin-bottom:8px; animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease 0.2s both;">
        일잘러 필수 상식
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height:1.6; animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease 0.3s both;">
        현장에서 매일 헷갈리는 세금 처리,<br>딱 정해드립니다!
      </div>
      <div style="
        margin-top:16px; 
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); 
        backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
        border-radius:14px; 
        padding:14px 16px;
        font-size:13px;
        font-weight:700;
        color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
        line-height:1.6;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease 0.4s both;
      ">
        🏗️ 세무서에 기장을 맡겨도, 현장에서 직접 챙겨야 하는 영수증 기준을 모르면 아까운 내 돈이 세금으로 줄줄 샙니다.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="height:16px;"></div>

  <!-- 카드 1: 식대 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#f97316;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:0s;">🍚</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#f97316;">1</span>
      식대의 진실
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"누구랑 밥을 먹었습니까?"</div>

    <div class="tax-item">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">👷</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:6px;">작업자/직원들과 먹은 밥</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">복리후생비 처리</div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <span class="tax-badge-ok">부가세 환급 ✅</span>
          <span class="tax-badge-ok">종소세 경비 ✅</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#16a34a; font-weight:800; margin-top:6px;">💚 가장 세금 혜택이 좋습니다!</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-item">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">🤝</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:6px;">거래처 소장님에게 밥을 샀을 때</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">접대비 처리</div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <span class="tax-badge-no">부가세 환급 ❌</span>
          <span class="tax-badge-ok">종소세 경비 ✅</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-item" style="background:#fef2f2;">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">🍱</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:6px;">나 홀로 현장 혼밥</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px;">개인 생활비 분류</div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <span class="tax-badge-no">부가세 환급 ❌</span>
          <span class="tax-badge-no">종소세 경비 ❌</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 2: 차량 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#3b82f6;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:0.3s;">🛻</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#3b82f6;">2</span>
      현장 차량 유지비
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"차종이 곧 돈입니다"</div>

    <div class="tax-item" style="background:#f0fdf4;">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">🚐</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:6px;">포터, 밴, 9인승 이상</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">스타리아, 카니발 등</div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <span class="tax-badge-ok">부가세 환급 ✅</span>
          <span class="tax-badge-ok">종소세 경비 ✅</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#16a34a; font-weight:700;">기름값, 수리비, 톨게이트비 전부 공제!</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-item" style="background:#fef2f2;">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">🚗</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:6px;">일반 승용차</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;">싼타페, 그랜저 등</div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <span class="tax-badge-no">부가세 공제 절대 불가 ❌</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#dc2626; font-weight:700;">⚠️ 짐을 아무리 실어도 부가세 공제 안 됩니다!</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 3: 폐기물 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#ef4444;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:0.6s;">🗑️</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#ef4444;">3</span>
      폐기물 처리비
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"현금 박치기의 치명적 함정"</div>

    <div class="tax-danger-box">
      <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#991b1b; margin-bottom:8px;">🚨 이런 말 들어보셨죠?</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#7f1d1d; font-weight:700; line-height:1.6; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); border-radius:10px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        "부가세 10% 별도니까 현금으로 하시죠~"
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
        ❌ 당장 10% 아끼려다 <span style="text-decoration:underline;">수백만 원 단위의 종합소득세 경비 처리</span>를 통째로 날립니다!
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-tip-box">
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#166534; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
        ✅ 덩치가 큰 비용일수록 무조건 10%를 더 내더라도 <strong>세금계산서</strong>를 끊어두는 것이 훨씬 이득입니다!
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 4: 간이영수증 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#eab308;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:0.9s;">🧾</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#eab308;">4</span>
      철물점 간이영수증
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"마지노선은 딱 3만 원"</div>

    <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="flex:1; background:#f0fdf4; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:6px;">✅</div>
        <div style="font-size:22px; font-weight:900; color:#166534;">3만원</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#16a34a; margin-top:4px;">이하 OK</div>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; background:#fef2f2; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:6px;">❌</div>
        <div style="font-size:22px; font-weight:900; color:#dc2626;">3만원 초과</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#dc2626; margin-top:4px;">2% 가산세 벌금</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-highlight-box">
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#1e40af; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
        💳 3만원 이상은 무조건 <strong>카드 결제</strong>나 <strong>지출증빙 현금영수증</strong>을 챙기세요!
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 5: 가족 인건비 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#10b981;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:1.2s;">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#10b981;">5</span>
      가족 인건비 처리
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"가장 합법적인 절세 치트키"</div>

    <div class="tax-item" style="background:#f0fdf4; border:1.5px solid #86efac;">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">🏆</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:8px;">배우자·가족을 정식 직원으로!</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px; color:#374151; font-weight:700; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:8px;">
          은행 업무, 세금계산서 발행, 전화 응대를 도와주는 가족을 <strong>정식 직원으로 등록</strong>하고 급여를 처리하세요.
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:13px; color:#16a34a; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
          ✨ 수익을 혼자 다 잡으면 누진세 폭등!<br>
          ✨ 가족 급여(경비)로 세금 구간 대폭 절감!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:#eff6ff; border-radius:10px; padding:10px 14px; margin-top:8px;">
      <div style="font-size:12px; color:#1e40af; font-weight:700;">📝 TIP: 간단한 업무 일지를 작성해 두면 완벽합니다!</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 6: 고가 장비 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#8b5cf6;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:1.5s;">🎥</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#8b5cf6;">6</span>
      고가의 장비와 공구
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"한 번에 털어낼 수 없습니다"</div>

    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="flex:1; background:#f9fafb; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:4px;">🔧</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:800; color:#111827;">일반 수공구</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-top:4px;">소모품비로 바로 처리</div>
        <span class="tax-badge-ok" style="margin-top:6px;">즉시 경비 ✅</span>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; background:#faf5ff; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:4px;">⚙️</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:800; color:#111827;">100만원↑ 장비</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:#6b7280; font-weight:700; margin-top:4px;">5년 감가상각 필요</div>
        <span class="tax-badge-warn" style="margin-top:6px;">분할 처리 ⚠️</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-highlight-box">
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#1e40af; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
        💡 부가세 환급은 구매 시 한 번에 다 받습니다! 경비 처리만 5년 분할입니다.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 카드 7: 인건비 -->
  <div class="tax-card" style="border-left-color:#0ea5e9;">
    <div class="tax-card-icon" style="animation-delay:1.8s;">👷‍♂️</div>
    <div class="tax-card-title">
      <span class="tax-card-number" style="background:#0ea5e9;">7</span>
      반장님들 일당
    </div>
    <div class="tax-card-subtitle">"가장 비중이 큰 필수 경비"</div>

    <div class="tax-item">
      <div style="font-size:24px; flex-shrink:0;">💪</div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#111827; margin-bottom:8px;">종합소득세 최강 경비!</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px; color:#374151; font-weight:700; line-height:1.6;">
          인건비는 부가가치세가 없는 항목이라 부가세 공제 개념 자체가 없습니다. 하지만 <strong>종소세를 줄여주는 가장 강력한 경비</strong>입니다.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tax-danger-box">
      <div style="font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; font-weight:800; line-height:1.6;">
        🚨 계좌이체만 하지 마세요!<br>
        <strong>3.3% 사업소득 또는 일용직 원천세 신고</strong>를 꼬박꼬박 하셔야 세금 폭탄을 피할 수 있습니다.
      </div>
    </div>
